    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<div class="page">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p><strong>Guidance for students and practice educators: How to work with a student who develops a health-related issue during practice placement</strong></p>
<div class="page">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p>Occupational therapy students, have a responsibility under the HCPC Guidance on Conduct and Ethics for Students to limit, or stop practice if their performance is affected by their health (HCPC 2016). Self declaration is dependent upon honesty and insight and disclosure, whilst not a legal obligation, is certainly an ethical and moral obligation.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></Value>
